<main>
<h1>Record your story</h1>
<p>Tell us about you, your favourite place in Islington, something that brings you joy, or rage, or simply something about Islington’s history others may not know about.</p>
<<button "Record">>
  <<goto "record">>
  <</button>>

</main>

<<include "footerback">>

:: record [nobr]
<<set $prevpass to "prerecord">>
<<set $passage to "record">>

<main>
<h1>Record</h1>
    <iframe src="https://www.speakpipe.com/widget/inline/2iawuy25u8ynlcssocfc003zmfcl529u" allow="microphone" width="100%" height="200" frameborder="0"></iframe>
<p>By clicking Record, you consent for your recording to be published online as part of the project. You can withdraw that consent at any time. More info can be found in our <a href="#" class="highlighted">terms of use</a> .</p>
<<button "Back to menu">>
  <<goto "map">>
  <</button>>

</main>
<<include "footerback">>